[
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "自然语言处理第二章 隐马尔科夫模型",
        "text_level": 2,
        "bbox": [
            238,
            292,
            758,
            551
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "马尔科夫模型 (Markov Model)",
        "text_level": 2,
        "bbox": [
            54,
            229,
            447,
            283
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "一最早由AndreiA.Markov，（切比雪夫Chebyshev的一个学生）于1913年提出，它的最原始目的是为了语言上的应用",
        "bbox": [
            89,
            290,
            940,
            383
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "● 隐马尔科夫模型(Hidden Markov Model，HMM)",
        "bbox": [
            54,
            388,
            633,
            442
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "－其数学思想是由Baum等人於1966\\~1970提出",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            450,
            577,
            496
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "一从某种意义上讲，HMM本身是一个马尔科夫过程的概率函数",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            501,
            764,
            550
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "在20世纪70年代被CMU的Baker以及IBM的Jelinek等人应用在了语音处理上",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            555,
            877,
            603
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "之后被广泛应用在了汉语自动分词、词性标注、统计机器翻译等很多方面",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            609,
            920,
            659
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "header",
        "text": "3.0 「 引信",
        "bbox": [
            28,
            64,
            156,
            112
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "header",
        "text": "",
        "bbox": [
            936,
            51,
            996,
            129
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "目录 Contents",
        "text_level": 2,
        "bbox": [
            44,
            187,
            181,
            305
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "3.1 马尔科夫模型  \n3.2 隐马尔科夫模型  \n3.3 HMM的三个基本问题",
        "bbox": [
            67,
            412,
            500,
            687
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "chart",
        "img_path": "images/2258c6f58b08e0e52e53efbc4f88c5c5957d21e2c6da5c85c7bd65759c3bf575.jpg",
        "content": "",
        "chart_caption": [],
        "chart_footnote": [],
        "bbox": [
            541,
            0,
            1000,
            1000
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "• Markov, 1913",
        "bbox": [
            165,
            242,
            334,
            279
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "• 随机过程",
        "bbox": [
            166,
            292,
            284,
            333
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "又称“随机函数”，是随时间而随机变化的过程",
        "bbox": [
            201,
            346,
            670,
            387
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "• 马尔科夫模型描述了一类重要的随机过程",
        "bbox": [
            166,
            400,
            576,
            442
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "设系统有N个状态 ${ \\cal S } = \\{ s _ { 1 } , s _ { 2 } , \\cdots , s _ { N } \\}$",
        "bbox": [
            196,
            481,
            522,
            529
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "随着时间的推移，系统将从某一状态转移到另一状态。",
        "bbox": [
            195,
            542,
            705,
            587
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$\\mathcal { Q } = \\{ q _ { 1 } , q _ { 2 } , \\cdots , q _ { T } \\}$ 为一随机变量序列， $\\textstyle q _ { t } \\in S , t = 1 , 2 , \\cdots , T$",
        "bbox": [
            196,
            603,
            721,
            650
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "则系统在时间t处于状态 $\\dot { s } _ { j }$ 的概率取决于其在时间1,2,…，t-1的状态",
        "bbox": [
            195,
            661,
            817,
            711
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "img_path": "images/3faa7cd84fab300ddd0ff8764b741f3049c073f9ab76c13efcf4bfa85bdbb242.jpg",
        "text": "$$\nP ( q _ { t } = s _ { j } \\mid q _ { t - 1 } = s _ { i } , q _ { t - 2 } = s _ { k } , \\cdots )\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            214,
            759,
            580,
            822
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "header",
        "text": "3.1 马尔科夫模型",
        "bbox": [
            28,
            62,
            256,
            112
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "header",
        "text": "",
        "bbox": [
            936,
            51,
            996,
            131
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "• 一阶马尔可夫过程",
        "text_level": 2,
        "bbox": [
            165,
            240,
            400,
            287
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "如果系统在t时间的状态只与其在时间t-1的状态相关，则该随机过程称为一阶马尔可夫过程",
        "bbox": [
            202,
            301,
            825,
            387
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "img_path": "images/83e7a829baef6110865c59fedf987d0be0deef848200d928faf80710bd708350.jpg",
        "text": "$$\nP ( q _ { t } = s _ { j } \\mid q _ { t - 1 } = s _ { i } , q _ { t - 2 } = s _ { k } , \\cdots ) \\approx P ( q _ { t } = s _ { j } \\mid q _ { t - 1 } = s _ { i } )\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            227,
            401,
            781,
            457
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "• 马尔可夫模型",
        "bbox": [
            166,
            466,
            347,
            512
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "独立于时间t的随机过程",
        "bbox": [
            202,
            527,
            446,
            568
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "img_path": "images/3faff5abf7736b3ffe05b707e8a8f9ed957e5879c26aba710066d9a7fffc7ff0.jpg",
        "text": "$$\nP ( q _ { t } = s _ { j } \\mid q _ { t - 1 } = s _ { i } ) = a _ { i j } , ( 1 \\leq i , j \\leq N )\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            213,
            590,
            571,
            642
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$a _ { i j }$ 称为状态转移概率",
        "bbox": [
            211,
            670,
            440,
            731
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$a _ { i j }$ 须满足以下条件",
        "bbox": [
            610,
            668,
            781,
            720
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "img_path": "images/a318b900654cd7f4da84c78543f3e4fc8eeb90eb63fedc42cbae9a207f890a1e.jpg",
        "text": "$$\na _ { i j } \\geq 0\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            638,
            735,
            696,
            781
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "img_path": "images/1858806d31d5f9714ce174ec509f552dea2723ecf292459adc1b0aa6c5268078.jpg",
        "text": "$$\n\\sum _ { j = 1 } ^ { N } a _ { i j } = 1\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            642,
            794,
            722,
            896
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "header",
        "text": "3.1 马尔科夫模型",
        "bbox": [
            29,
            62,
            256,
            112
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "header",
        "text": "",
        "bbox": [
            936,
            51,
            996,
            131
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
